Brown Butter Rice Krispie Treats
  --GIR

1/2 c butter
16 oz package mini marshmallows
2 tbsp bourbon (or vanilla for kid safe)
1 tsp sea salt
8 c crispy rice cereal

Melt butter in a saucepan over medium heat, stirring constantly, until golden brown and has a nutty aroma, ~5 min. Add marshmallows, reduce heat to medium low, and cook, stirring occasionally, until marshmallows are melted, 3-4 min. Stir in bourbon and salt into mixture and remove from heat. Add cereal to marshmallow and mix until cereal is evenly coated; transfer to 9x13" baking dish. (optional) Place silicon mat over top and press down into dish. Cool treats to room temp, at least 30 min. Cut and serve.
